      "comment": "SUPERIOR STRIDE (5) is progressing strongly having recorded two big wins along with a fifth in the NSW Derby from his last three starts here. Led from this barrier and cruised home by 19m over this distance last start. Could be hard to catch off that. WHAT THE TOOTH (6) continues to race consistently having put five placings together. Has ground to make up on SUPERIOR STRIDE through his second two back but beat that rival home when third in the NSW Derby prior. GLADIATRIX (9) was back in the winners' list when she led throughout last start. Draws out but overcame the outside barrier to win the NSW Oaks at this circuit and distance last month. CEE CEE IN PARIS (8) draws wide but can be competitive after her second to GLADIATRIX last start.",
